==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oxalis
<hw>Ox"a*lis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a kind of
sorrel, Gr. <grk>'oxali`s</grk>, fr. <grk>'oxy`s</grk> sharp, pungent,
acid.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of plants, mostly herbs,
with acid-tasting trifoliolate or multifoliolate leaves; -- called also
<altname>wood sorrel</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

